Title: Gonte - MyWpfControls
Description:
MyWpfControls tries to make it easier for developers to create WPF applications. 
It's developed in C#

This project requires the binary file MyUtilities.dll found in the project Gonte - MyUtilities
HomeWiki:
MyWpfControls

Features:

- View model support for a tree view control
- Asynchronous command class to execute background tasks
